North American Biologicals Inc said it hasreceived a 10 mln dlr credit facility from Manufacturers andTraders Trust Co of Buffalo, N.Y.    It said the new credit would replace an existing 4.4 mlndlr line with Barclays PLC &lt;BCS.L>, and due to more favorableinterest rates, borrowing costs should be significantlyreduced.    The company said half of the credit is designated for usein acquisitions.  It said it expects to conclude anacquisition, possibly outside its plasma and serum field, byyear-end. Reuter&#3;